cu.error_type: unreachable elements or wrong routing definitions
cu.explanation_en: Changing the GNB IPv4 address for NG-AMF to an unreachable IP (10.0.0.1) will prevent proper routing and connectivity to the AMF, causing network attachment failures and configuration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Modifying the T1a_cp_dl timing parameters to [286, 430] introduces inconsistency in downlink timing alignment, potentially causing synchronization issues, data transmission errors, and system faults in the DU.
